# Job Application Automator

An intelligent, fully automated job application pipeline built with n8n, 
Gemini AI, and Google Sheets. This workflow runs daily, finds relevant 
AI Automation roles, scores them using AI, generates tailored cover 
letters, and applies automatically.

---

## What It Does

- Scrapes jobs daily from 7 sources including LinkedIn, Indeed, 
  Remotive, WeWorkRemotely, Himalayas, Remoteok, and Arbeitnow
- Filters jobs by location (Remote and Nigeria) and role keywords
- Uses Gemini AI to score each job from 1 to 10 based on skill match,
  location fit, seniority, and apply URL availability
- Auto-applies to jobs scoring 6 and above with a tailored cover letter
- Flags complex or low-scoring jobs to a Manual Review sheet
- Logs all applications to Google Sheets with status, score, and reason
- Sends a daily Gmail summary of all activity

---

## Workflow Architecture

| Node | Purpose |
|---|---|
| Daily Trigger 2PM Lagos | Fires every day at 2pm Lagos time |
| Global Config | Stores personal details, target roles, regions |
| Source 1 - Remotive | Scrapes remote tech jobs via RSS |
| Source 2 - WeWorkRemotely | Scrapes remote jobs via RSS |
| Source 3 - Himalayas | Scrapes remote jobs via RSS |
| Source 4 - Remoteok | Pulls jobs via JSON API |
| Source 5 - Arbeitnow | Pulls jobs via free API |
| Source 6 - Arbeitnow 2 | Secondary Arbeitnow feed |
| Source 7 - JSearch | Pulls LinkedIn and Indeed jobs via RapidAPI |
| Merge All Sources | Combines all 7 sources into one stream |
| Normalise All Sources | Converts all data into unified job objects |
| Geo Filter | Keeps only Remote, Nigeria, US, UK jobs |
| Job Role Filter | Keeps only automation related roles |
| Prep AI Scoring Prompt | Builds the Gemini scoring prompt per job |
| Gemini AI Scorer | Sends each job to Gemini for scoring |
| Parse Gemini Score | Extracts score, reason, and apply URL |
| Score Filter | Routes high scoring jobs to Track A, low to Track B |
| Cover Letter Generator | Generates tailored cover letter using Gemini AI |
| Log Applied Jobs | Logs auto-applied jobs to Google Sheets |
| Daily Summary Email | Sends Gmail summary of all applications |
| Flag for Manual Review | Logs low scoring jobs to Manual Review sheet |

---

## Tools and APIs Used

- n8n (self-hosted workflow automation)
- Google Gemini AI (gemini-3-flash-preview model)
- JSearch API via RapidAPI (LinkedIn and Indeed jobs)
- Google Sheets (application tracking)
- Gmail (daily summary emails)
- Remotive RSS, WeWorkRemotely RSS, Himalayas RSS
- Remoteok JSON API, Arbeitnow API

---

## How to Use

1. Import the workflow JSON into your n8n instance
2. Update the Global Config node with your personal details
3. Add your Gemini API key to the Gemini AI Scorer node
4. Add your JSearch RapidAPI key to Source 7
5. Connect your Google Sheets and Gmail credentials
6. Activate the workflow and let it run daily

